OOC: Yeah, they're on earth, but prehistoric earth. Just find
something for her to go back through time and bingo!

BIC:

Prophetus let out of a terrible roar as he looked powerless at the
freighter going up and away. Finally, he decided to renounce. The
tigress was not worth it after all.

> OK.. cool. :) 
> 
> > 
> > BIC:
> > 
> > Prophetus was furious. He blasted his way through the ceiling of the
> > vault and started climbing to the surface.

> > ARE ALONE AND WILL BE FOREVER! EVEN PREDACONS WILL REJECT YOU!

> > He swung a huge bladed tail towards her.
> >

> She heard him, but would not listen. She understood she was the
last, which 
> made it all the more special & important. 
> 
> Her own memories of the world came to her, as she rushed along
towards the 
> surface. But not fast enough for her. 
> 
> Eventually, she made it to the surface & made a beeline to the
spaceport. 
> There she searched for a chip to take off with. Anything.. but
before hand, 
> she hacked into one of the computers nearby... albeit short, as she
gathered 
> what info would be helpful. 
> 
> Predacons.. upon a planet. She got the coordinates. 
> 
> Then left the comp quickly. She didn't want to get anything that
would be 
> damaging. 
> 
> She spotted a ship that looked like a fast ship, even though it was
possibly 
> a freighter. She wished she was in her old form, she could possibly
make it 
> to the world where the Predacons were. 
> 
> Running into the ship, she went to the cockpit, where she reved it
up, within 
> minutes, she blasted off. She had to leave. But swore she would
return. & 
> return with a new Decpeticon army to recapture Cybertron under the
RIGHTFUL 
> conquerers. 
> 
> The ship, with some supplies in it hold, took off, darting away from 
> Cybertron. 
> 
> It's destination... Earth (I hope this is the planet where they are on.)
